# {{PROJECT_TITLE}}

A full-stack monorepo powered by [BENT Stack](https://github.com/casey-clayton/create-bent-stack) — Bun + Elysia + Next.js + Turbo with Prisma, Better Auth, and end-to-end type safety via Eden Treaty.

## Getting Started

```bash
# Install dependencies
bun install

# Set up environment
cp .env.example .env

# Push database schema
bun run db:push

# Start development servers
bun run dev
```

